President Uhuru Kenyatta has sent a message of comfort to the family of Cabinet Secretary Sicily Kariuki. This is following the passing away of her daughter Wendy Muthoni today at a Nairobi hospital after two weeks of hospitalization. "I wish the family God's fortitude during this difficult period of grief and assure them of my support as they come to terms with the big loss, Uhuru said. The CS lost her daughter today at a Nairobi hospital. The cause of death is still not known.